  <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">1. What products do you offer?</div>
    <div class="answer">We offer a wide range of optical products and accessories including eyewear, watches, wallets, belts, and more.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">2. Do you offer prescription eyewear?</div>
    <div class="answer">Yes, we provide prescription eyewear. You can select your desired frame and provide your prescription details during checkout.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">3. How do I track my order?</div>
    <div class="answer">Once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking number via email. You can use this tracking number to monitor the status of your delivery.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">4. What is your return policy?</div>
    <div class="answer">We offer a hassle-free return policy. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you can return it within 30 days for a full refund.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">5. Are your products authentic?</div>
    <div class="answer">Yes, we guarantee the authenticity of all our products. We source them directly from reputable manufacturers and distributors.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">6. Do you offer international shipping?</div>
    <div class="answer">Yes, we offer international shipping to many countries. Shipping rates and delivery times may vary depending on the destination.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">7. How can I contact customer support?</div>
    <div class="answer">You can reach our customer support team via email at omgenterprise1810gmail.com. We strive to respond to all inquiries promptly.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">8. Are your products covered by warranty?</div>
    <div class="answer">Yes, most of our products come with a manufacturer's warranty. Please refer to the product description or contact us for warranty details.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">9. Can I cancel my order?</div>
    <div class="answer">You can cancel your order if it has not been shipped yet. Please contact us as soon as possible to request a cancellation.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-item">
    <div class="question">10. How do I change my account information?</div>
    <div class="answer">You can update your account information by logging into your account on our website and navigating to the profile or settings section.</div>
  </div>

